<DATE>
<P>
June 1, 1989, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 8; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
462 words 
</P>
