<P>
DIGEST /LOCAL NEWS IN BRIEF: BERNARDI ENDORSED BY RIVAL FROM PRIMARY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jules Bagneris, who ran against Los Angeles Councilman Ernani Bernardi in the 
