SAN GABRIEL VALLEY DIGEST: DUARTE; 
</P>
<P>
3 RECYCLING WINNERS PICKED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Three winners have been named in the first drawing of the Resource Revolution 
Riches program sponsored by the city in an effort to promote recycling in the 
community. 
</P>
<P>
Up to five Duarte families may be awarded prizes weekly after drawings of 
randomly selected addresses where the families participate in the city's free 
recycling program. 
</P>
<P>
The families of Charles Belling, Karen Olson and Beth van Leuven won six months 
of free refuse service. They are now eligible for a $260 quarterly cash drawing 
and a seven-day Hawaiian vacation drawing next May. 
</P>
