touch off a bench-clearing brawl during the seventh inning of the Dodgers' 9-4 
victory Wednesday. ; Photo, Umpire Bill Hohn tries to restrain Hubie Brooks, 
who was hit by Orel Hershiser's pitch. JAYNE KAMIN-ONCEA / Los Angeles Times 
